Freedom: Atlanta Pop Festival is an upcoming posthumous live album by The Jimi
Hendrix Experience, documenting their July 4, 1970 performance at the Atlanta
International Pop Festival. It will feature sixteen songs recorded during their
evening performance. The album is scheduled for release on August 28, 2015, in
conjunction with the Jimi Hendrix video documentary, Jimi Hendrix: Electric Church.
